## .DS_Store and similar files are automatically excluded by R CMD build

## GitHub files
## ========================================
^\.github$

## R/RStudio files
## ========================================
## .Rdata and .Rhistory are automatically excluded by R CMD build
^.*\.Rproj$
^\.Rproj\.user$


## Package development
## ========================================
^_pkgdown\.yml$
^data-raw$
^LICENSE\.md$
^cran-comments\.md$

